Planning to visit Talk:House Restaurant?
Here are some parking tips to make your experience smooth and enjoyable!
We have on-site parking behind the restaurant on NW Australian Street.
If that’s full, don’t worry! There’s overflow parking at the corner of NW Palm Street and NW Dixie Highway.
And after 5 PM, you can park at the offices next door!
We want you to focus on enjoying your meal without the parking stress.

Our Story
/$
$
At Talk House, our story began with a passion for creating unforgettable dining experiences. Located just outside downtown Stuart, Florida, our restaurant offers a formal yet casual atmosphere with indoor and outdoor seating options. Our chef Dave is a recognized culinary expert in the community, known for his unique and delicious dishes. Come visit us and become a part of our story.
/$
/$
/$
$
$
/$
/$
/$
$
$
$
$
In the Kitchen
/$
$
Our approach in the kitchen is simple - we use only the freshest, locally-sourced ingredients to craft our dishes. Our team of culinary experts works tirelessly to create unique and delicious flavor combinations that will keep you coming back for more. Whether you're looking for a romantic dinner for two or a fun night out with friends, Talk House is the perfect destination for any occasion.
